pwd: Show the current directory (Print working directory)
ls: List files and directories
cd directoryname: Change to a directory
cd ..: Move up one directory levelmkdir directoryname: Create a new directory
rmdir directoryname: Remove an empty directory
rm filename: Remove an empty directory
rm -r directoryname: Remove a directory and its contents
cp file1 file2: copy a file
mv file1 file2: Move or rename a file
touch filename: Create a new empty file